Television personalities are trying to get to the bottom of the coronavirus broadcasts — by not wearing any.
A video montage compiled by John Oliver’s “Last Week Tonight” contains dozens of clips of local news anchors across the country asking colleagues and guests on-air, “Are you wearing pants?”“I do have pants on.
Are you wearing pants these days?
Oliver: I’m wearing sweatpants (Oliver stands up to show off a dark pair with zippered pockets.)
I’m wearing a suit, but I’m not wearing shoes.